自己温ielts如果唔係你預英文會退步到仆街</blockquote><br />\n考左三次都係2啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有咩辦法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0080842c00dea4f6734e2723e3088f7694b869e","tid":318271,"uid":26528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底"},{"pid":"7f766c8d26be0acfed4b897b8e5e69dd959ba51b","tid":318271,"uid":65071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁考多次都衰英文可以點<br />\n台灣又多科選擇<br />\n有小小想去台灣讀cs</blockquote><br />\n衰英文 你過到台灣英文會更加差 除非會自己温ielts如果唔係你預英文會退步到仆街</blockquote><br />\n考左三次都係2啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有咩辦法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考左三次都2 就算啦 好明顯係能力既問題 去邊都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bc18a68c87826566569135a2361237c76bd76c","tid":318271,"uid":62299,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n<br />\n去台灣讀U?人地係人都入到咁仲叫U<br />\n冇人認受一地野雞"},{"pid":"97860ece1f6a61abc3bde4fdb24f91d43a49bd2c","tid":318271,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"非台大不了。"},{"pid":"90791d51a13a70e23b47fa5bc7b5e0e21f12b7d7","tid":318271,"uid":6972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n你真係洗緊底？"},{"pid":"61e057ce37c4b0a00b8c104d2f629b00a784e362","tid":318271,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"真係咪撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2308889d33b12713c306ceb203d5922056a09575","tid":318271,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"係台灣讀緊art同philosophy<br />\n老師既質素會有啲參差 <br />\n係為興趣讀既就無咩所謂，你地想四年之後靠張沙紙搵工真係無可能<br />\n真係去左既，諗下點讀master洗底或者用四年去學一技之長啦<br />\n利申 出黎都唔知做咩 最多教下小朋友咁"},{"pid":"eb9e9242cdd5417b1fad09383a0d4aa007acf231","tid":318271,"uid":29130,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"張沙紙無咩用就真既<br />\n<br />\n但台灣生活個4年我好開心，無後悔過<br />\n<br />\n利申 台北「最高學府」濕勁文科"},{"pid":"d4bc04f8a5d2564a0b7049695ba8264ab1e8a680","tid":318271,"uid":60376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"睇下咩科 中醫果d都算係咁"},{"pid":"9e24b3e1144d3ff9e9c6356e670c7d25f475e5d7","tid":318271,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多"},{"pid":"8591beddb858d935fd90e6eb0f757489f4853bcc","tid":318271,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n你真係洗緊底？</blockquote><br />\n讀完仲廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3e1d2151796576fe44fd44d7b32cdbe728d6ad","tid":318271,"uid":15471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張沙紙無咩用就真既<br />\n<br />\n但台灣生活個4年我好開心，無後悔過<br />\n<br />\n利申 台北「最高學府」濕勁文科</blockquote><br />\n咁你不如每年申請去wh好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dda98f31c38cb5d698e727aa54cbf92cdb6ea8","tid":318271,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題 <br />\n台狗戇鳩鳩唔在講 台妹無想像中咁純都無謂提<br />\n唔好以為讀到台灣所謂五大就好威<br />\n人地台灣僱主見你唔係本地人已經唔會考慮<br />\n成功係個邊定居係好少數例子<br />\n識好多朋友讀所謂五大甚至台大都係返黎乞食<br />\n而且你dse唔係有返咁上下過到去都係讀唔掂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上年16.5分入五大讀電機條傻鳩依加讀到就黎quit U</span><br />\n有返咁上下既應屆考生我建議你都係讀local好好多<br />\n差少少既朋友讀asso上返去啦 過台灣都係曬錢曬時間</blockquote><br />\n唔好以前靠DSE成績入得到呢科，就等於讀得掂先得架<br />\n電機呢啲科出名難，憑果16.5分，放棄U life 都未必讀得掂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5822d19f643b86b3ed957515524927947433f87c","tid":318271,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"點解16.5入到五大電機？"},{"pid":"d29c734abed4857e4b1c4859c27f0aeae86ae335","tid":318271,"uid":126897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留左喺英國做野."},{"pid":"11060fcfb79ed2d5768ec9cd05230c93e1b3e5be","tid":318271,"uid":49935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"台大 日文點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da18faecc3669dd870c5f621dca0e74e99ab1b28","tid":318271,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留左喺英國做野.</blockquote><br />\n洗底係完全無問題<br />\n不過與其係咁，當初點解唔直接去澳洲、英國讀"},{"pid":"959918216314bc7f008ee4476b5e615c919b385a","tid":318271,"uid":4917,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台大 日文點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去日本讀啦"},{"pid":"3661222e964cfaa574ea5e333282c037f1220b06","tid":318271,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留左喺英國做野.</blockquote><br />\n洗底係完全無問題<br />\n不過與其係咁，當初點解唔直接去澳洲、英國讀</blockquote><br />\n咪係 <br />\n又要特登哂錢哂時間去Tw 讀degree"},{"pid":"9b8d2d7deb01f5d85ebcc0d798a8a02b4f57a1c0","tid":318271,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留