/blockquote><br />\n留台唔番來食女ok<br />\n<br />\n番來考執業試就pk"},{"pid":"d8c19c1d27f10fbe1146d0b09335f5a91314e61b","tid":318271,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台大 日文點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去日本讀啦</blockquote><br />\n[sosad台灣讀日文極on9</blockquote><br />\n你去日本讀仲好，讀書生活度度都迫住你用日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8466c84d375c7f0056f45132bb27f4953730bf","tid":318271,"uid":49935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台大 日文點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去日本讀啦</blockquote><br />\n[sosad台灣讀日文極on9</blockquote><br />\n你去日本讀仲好，讀書生活度度都迫住你用日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台大喎 台灣最高學府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a822022d221f8f3de8ae8b6167252a37b6d1654","tid":318271,"uid":47250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"曾經係放榜前報左台灣既私立，放左榜之後揀返本地既hd, 個時中學個升學主任知道左之後話：「都好啊有hd 讀，不過台灣有degree 你又唔去讀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩今年non ju上返ugc, 而當年我既同班同學有一半都去左台灣，但無可否認佢地讀個4年係一定開心過留係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7672a50f3841aafa53419570ba44ba80fd981d81","tid":318271,"uid":4328,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:27:27.000Z","msg":"係識發光嘅，去邊都會發光。<br />\n唔識發光嘅，一世都係垃圾。"},{"pid":"bc99fcf3c8005c532bf8b09e29040574ee62f50a","tid":318271,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係識發光嘅，去邊都會發光。<br />\n唔識發光嘅，一世都係垃圾。</blockquote><br />\n台大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7245731659b2f9678f9d8a7efde5a28b0dd4b5ce","tid":318271,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"唔可以去讀碩士洗底咩？"},{"pid":"23a8f3a9bb9e07abd656dd59b2a16ff0213c319a","tid":318271,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:05:12.000Z","msg":"成班友以為台大日文最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4618579cabc24ee8c321088878ac52d6de9975fb","tid":318271,"uid":25689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"想係台灣搵食<br />\n唔該去讀EE 個類 畢業一定有人請<br />\n你讀咩人文 地理 文科既<br />\n算撚數啦<br />\n文科本身就係垃圾 就算你讀台成交清都係垃圾黎<br />\n仲有讀完4年<br />\n你可以去埋外國讀埋master番黎都得<br />\n去台灣讀唔係無用<br />\n但係如果你諗住去讀文科個類 咩撚野旅遊 飲食 算撚數啦 你都預左呢4年係垃圾架啦<br />\n建議你係香港讀<br />\n想去讀既話<br />\n一係就讀醫 或者ee個類<br />\n畢完業 輕鬆係台灣搵到野做"},{"pid":"f5f10814f4db3ce3088e1a9d30af20c40d7ff6ea","tid":318271,"uid":61077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"最佳玩法<br />\n搵一科英國同美國認既科<br />\n<br />\n去台灣屌4年台妹<br />\n返英美master洗底"},{"pid":"686567fa6ad9715bf911268252471a1784d20c2e","tid":318271,"uid":26528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留左喺英國做野.</blockquote><br />\n洗底係完全無問題<br />\n不過與其係咁，當初點解唔直接去澳洲、英國讀</blockquote><br />\n咪係 <br />\n又要特登哂錢哂時間去Tw 讀degree</blockquote><br />\n學費平幾多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗底再去英國、澳洲唔使錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣私立大學 大慨半年4萬台幣<br />\n依家澳洲讀緊16k澳紙半年<br />\n依家讀緊個degree 年半就畢到業<br />\n當然啦，我係到留言主要係唔想有人再去台灣讀大學。"},{"pid":"a9963dd7a1242be4876fc8e43d62b887c7e6ae0d","tid":318271,"uid":87230,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"後生仔有咩所謂<br />\n玩幾年再慢慢番黎捱世界都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec1b5b0a34cc5582ae88ee8cd1d96774e900e49","tid":318271,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efb22a12d438329d43bf2350caaf13558cab5e5","tid":318271,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d560e48969e6687e1cef6109354be241e4fdf57","tid":318271,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後生仔有咩所謂<br />\n玩幾年再慢慢番黎捱世界都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚伏鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb39fbed51a895db1fc7536f498e5c909d3a792","tid":318271,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳畢業，依家係澳洲讀緊master洗底</blockquote><br />\n我識人去左台灣讀大學, 然後去左英國讀master, 後來仲留左喺英國做野.</blockquote><br />\n洗底係完全無問題<br />\n不過與其係咁，當初點解唔直接去澳洲、英國讀</blockquote><br />\n咪係 <br />\n又要特登哂錢哂時間去Tw 讀degree</blockquote><br />\n學費平幾多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗底再去英國、澳洲唔使錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣私立大學 大慨半年4萬台幣<br />\n依家澳洲讀緊16k澳紙半年<br />\n依家讀緊個degree 年半就畢到業<br />\n當然啦，我係到留言主要係唔想有人再去台灣讀大學。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次我出撚完類似個post,宜家又有人loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb142f0ca58bd355f6dfd5ec2e8f2303528854a","tid":318271,"uid":3112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想係台灣搵食<br />\n唔該去讀EE 個類 畢業一定有人請<br />\n你讀咩人文 地理 文科既<br />\n算撚數啦<br />\n文科本身就係垃圾 就算你讀台成交清都係垃圾黎<br />\n仲有讀完4年<br />\n你可以去埋外國讀埋master番黎都得<br />\n去台灣讀唔係無用<br />\n但係如果你諗住去讀文科個類 咩撚野旅遊 飲食 算撚數啦 你都預左呢4年係垃圾架啦<br />\n建議你係香港讀<br />\n想去讀既話<br />\n一係就讀醫 或者ee個類<br />\n畢完業 輕鬆係台灣搵到野做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所言極是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係年年最多人讀都係一類組<br />\n<br />\n老實講,台灣最弱就係social science 同 business,如果讀humanities你當返黎報pgde 又好,出國再讀上去既話都冇問題,但係soc sci 同 business 我打死都留係香港,香港呢兩個field 不嬲都係相當唔錯,even 非三大<br />\n<br />\n醫療科就要留意返會唔會考慮回流香港,會既就要考慮下資格認可果D野<br />\n<br />\n理科工科就唔駛多講,台灣最多資源擺落去,尤其物理同電機,台大物理/電機&gt;&gt;三大物理/電機 (undergrad 計)"},{"pid":"2fd877e6074bfd71fa9f070ae19dd26e91ed4f1f","tid":318271,"uid":118867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"台灣?你係讀獸醫先好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1593ee1f90b4ad6fb01368870aa0138590651a6e","tid":318271,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想係台灣搵食<br />\n唔該去讀EE 個類 畢業一定有人請<br />\n你讀咩人文 地理 文科既<br />\n算撚數啦<br />\n文科本身就係垃圾 就算你讀台成交清都係垃圾黎<br />\n仲有讀完4年<br />\n你可以去埋外國讀埋master番黎都得<br />\n去台灣讀唔係無用<br />\n但係如果你諗住去讀文科個類 咩撚野旅遊 飲食 算撚數啦 你都預左呢4年係垃圾架啦<br />\n建議你係香港讀<br />\n想去讀既話<br />\n一係就讀醫 或者ee個類<br />\n畢完業 輕鬆